---
description: Solidity contract guidance
globs:
    - "contracts/src/**/*"
    - "contracts/test/**/*"
    - "contracts/script/**/*"
    - "test/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Prioritize escrow safety, access control, reentrancy resistance, gas awareness,
event coverage, and audit-ready clarity. Run Hardhat and Foundry tests after
contract changes. Do not introduce upgradeability or oracle dependencies without
a documented design and explicit tests.
